description:
I was walking thru the zoo and saw this sign.  The angle and the color caught my eye.  It made me think about how everyone is telling us what to do.  Or the counter to that ‚Ä¶ Stay on the Path ‚Ä¶ hang in there.

Also, all of the other signs were perfectly aligned and standing straight up.  But this one sign, just this one, was a rebel.
